{"tid":1627384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議聽日安排！","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:59:30.000Z","uid":239577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"df6dd1046e9d480077015c46a64f7f82dad4a95e","tid":1627384,"uid":239577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"到依家都仲未確實到聽日去邊<br />\n係度我有少少建議<br />\n我建議聽日全部人一齊去遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊塞爆佢老母！<br />\n雖然話兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n但係聽日不論安全同策略上都係一齊去同一個地方好啲<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日和理非同勇武分開做<br />\n班狗就會更加容易部署<br />\n因為咁樣勇武就冇左和理非嘅保護<br />\n而且人數亦都會因為分散而大大減少<br />\n對於進攻同走佬都十分不利<br />\n令班狗可以唔理和理非個度 <br />\n主要去十八區圍捕！<br />\n勇武俾佢地捉曬嘅機會好大！<br />\n<br />\n加上聽日一定要好似8.18個日咁和平散去<br />\n當俾大家休息下又好 俾全世界見到香港人仲渴望和平解決嘅一面又好<br />\n如果條柒婆都仲係冇反應 10.7就可以名正言順咁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩大佢！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我最想就係冇人再被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無論你係和理非定係勇武<br />\n更何況勇武依家已經越捉越少<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔該！！<br />\n一定要帶衫變裝！己經過左4個月 咁基本點解都仲未做到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"61f39fdb929c9accad0ba58b4321ef933b04fe11","tid":1627384,"uid":239577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7355d7d2f657ca20b4b063160b6c58e99bdd62d6","tid":1627384,"uid":239577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a43e869b7d6201ed2cfb7ac46724201d39a30f","tid":1627384,"